<p>
    Make sure you spell the names of electromagnetic waves correctly, especially <strong>infrared</strong>.
</p>

<h5>
    Proper Diction
</h5>
<ul>
    <li>
        When discussing the <strong>energy</strong> or <strong>frequency</strong> of an electromagnetic wave,
        we always write that it becomes <strong>higher</strong> or <strong>lower</strong>.
    </li>
    <li>
        When discussing the <strong>wavelength</strong> of an electromagnetic wave,
        we always write that it becomes <strong>longer</strong> or <strong>shorter</strong>.
    </li>
</ul>